              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.Neutron irradiation fields was noted and",
                " induced activities was measured including the",
                " contributions of scattered low-energy neutrons, the",
                " fluctuation of the neutron fluence rate during",
                " irradiation, the true coincidence sum effect, the",
                " random coincidence sum effect, the deviation in the",
                " measuring position due to finite sample thickness,",
                " the self-absorption of the gamma-ray in the sample",
